INDEPENDENCE DAY SPEECH BY HIS EXCELLENCY MUHAMMADU BUHARI PRESIDENT OF THE FEDERAL REPUBLIC OF NIGERIA ON THE OCCASION OF THE 59TH INDEPENDENCE ANNIVERSARY 1st OCTOBER, 2019 Dear Compatriots, 1st October each year is an opportunity for us to reflect and thank God for his endless blessings on our country. SECURITY: ACCELERATING SUSTAINABLE AND INCLUSIVE ECONOMY GROWTH FIGHTING CORRUPTION AND RESTORING GOOD GOVERNANCE: